= Setup

For manual installation:

```sh
git clone http://github.com/clemera/ivy-explorer.git
```
Add this to your init file:

```elisp
(add-to-list 'load-path "/<path-to>/ivy-explorer/")
(require 'ivy-explorer)
;; use ivy explorer for all file dialogs
(ivy-explorer-mode)
```